{"tid":2199587,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"這星期給香港人的通識題 - 陳沛敏","createTime":"2020-09-12T10:20:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T10:25:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0c41266b0c661585751d3a512cae929096e030ab","tid":2199587,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T10:20:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200912/IBHU4QZSOBE3NHL7LDCGXSZ3SA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200912%2FIBHU4QZSOBE3NHL7LDCGXSZ3SA%2F&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f6wVmkNCIo3TbJkxuaymrXU%3D&h=aee72470\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200912%2FIBHU4QZSOBE3NHL7LDCGXSZ3SA%2F&h=7538d742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200912/IBHU4QZSOBE3NHL7LDCGXSZ3SA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n這星期給香港人的通識題 - 陳沛敏<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dTgwDi16cAnXAQTULawq4gcA8uQ=/690x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DH3RUWTNZZEV7BPZ6AG2JBUGJA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdTgwDi16cAnXAQTULawq4gcA8uQ%3D%2F690x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDH3RUWTNZZEV7BPZ6AG2JBUGJA.jpg&h=0c3c9db8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下哪一樣事件，會引起你憎恨、藐視香港特區政府？<br />\n<br />\nA. 路過一個街站，聽到一名叫譚得志又名「快必」的男子，呼喊「反抗」、「五大訴求， 缺一不可」、「解散警隊，刻不容緩」、「721唔見人，831打死人」、「光復香港，時代革命」、「黑警死全家」、「打倒共產黨」等等語句。<br />\n<br />\nB. 多名防暴警察在旺角鬧市圍捕一名12歲女童，把她撲倒地上，以膝頭壓在女童身上予以制服。女童的哥哥在旁扯着女童衣服，也遭制止。家住旺角的女童媽媽說，當時子女想到油麻地文具店買上學用的顏料，女兒遇到持棍警察呼喝驚慌跑開，未料卻遭追捕膝壓，事後更被控違反限聚令。<br />\n<br />\nC. 有人遊行，大批防暴站出馬路截查。正駕駛970號新巴的車長為避警察、人群，多次響號示意，警方指車長「無故響號」，挑釁，嚴重影響現場警務人員工作，更指巴士「快速行駛」貼近警員，以危險駕駛罪將車長即場拘捕。事後又以車長持有士巴拿，指他藏有攻擊性武器。<br />\n<br />\n新巴事後翻查巴士行車紀錄，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》大部份黃絲讀者當然會答B and C；。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至於藍絲讀者，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n政權以言入罪，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n警察辯稱12歲女童逃跑，「形跡可疑」所以追捕。香港人即反問，7.21當晚元朗大批白衣人持藤條棍棒在街上聚集遊走，警方為何不覺「形跡可疑」。「驅趕」白衣人只需拍膊頭，為何對付12歲女卻要幾個防暴圍堵撲倒膝壓。<br />\n<br />\n香港警隊此等行徑經海外傳媒廣泛報道，。。。。。。"},{"pid":"3dee8a318651d10c33468ef1d6e9d42f5c31b361","tid":2199587,"uid":60539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T10:24:24.000Z","msg":"預左會越來越高壓管治<br />\n但呢個時候香港人應該每人行一小步<br />\n而唔係少部份人行好多步<br />\n只有齊上齊落港共先無我地乎"},{"pid":"af73637c2eeb2ed773f9468d749d266471eb7867","tid":2199587,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dee8a318651d10c33468ef1d6e9d42f5c31b361","tid":2199587,"uid":60539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T10:24:24.000Z","msg":"預左會越來越高壓管治<br />\n但呢個時候香港人應該每人行一小步<br />\n而唔係少部份人行好多步<br />\n只有齊上齊落港共先無我地乎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T10:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}